---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Martin Way for People"
  description="How we handle your data."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>

<main id="main-content" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
  <a href="/" class="text-sm text-muted hover:text-ink underline mb-8 inline-block">← Back to main page</a>

  <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-10">Effective March 4, 2026</p>

  <div class="space-y-10 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">What we collect</h2>
      <p>When you sign up for comment notifications, we collect your <strong class="text-ink">email address</strong>. We also store a <strong class="text-ink">one-way hash of your IP address</strong> to prevent abuse. We do not store your raw IP address.</p>
      <p class="mt-2">This site does not use cookies, analytics, or tracking of any kind.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">How we use it</h2>
      <p>Your email address is used for one purpose: to notify you when the public comment window opens for the Martin Way land-use appeal. We will not send marketing emails or share your address with third parties for their own use.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Where your data lives</h2>
      <p>Email addresses and IP hashes are stored in a <strong class="text-ink">Cloudflare D1</strong> database. Notification emails are sent through <strong class="text-ink">Resend</strong>. Both services process data on our behalf and are not permitted to use it for their own purposes.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">How long we keep it</h2>
      <p>We retain your email address until you unsubscribe or the appeal process concludes, whichever comes first. After that, we delete all subscriber data.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Your choices</h2>
      <p>You can request removal of your data at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:martinwayforpeople@pm.me" class="text-data underline">martinwayforpeople@pm.me</a>. We will delete your record within 5 business days.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">We do not sell your data</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with anyone for commercial purposes.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>If we change this policy, we will update the effective date above. Material changes will be noted on the site.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p><a href="mailto:martinwayforpeople@pm.me" class="text-data underline">martinwayforpeople@pm.me</a></p>
    </section>

  </div>
</main>

</BaseLayout>
